?name: First Last
!Nspace { ?name: John, !MoreNspace { ?name: Doe } }

no-options ::
{
	\a\b\f\n\r\t\v\x00\u1234\U43210987\e\s\0 //escaped-chars
	   some text   with spaces   //and a comment
	   
	My name is ^name!
	
	I know ^Nspace.name.
	I also know who ^Nspace.MoreNspace.name is.
	
	Escape ^ without ent is valid.
}

